          <li class="feat-row"><span class="fi fi-yes">✓</span> AI descriptions (unlimited)</li>
          <li class="feat-row"><span class="fi fi-yes">✓</span> Advanced scheduling</li>
          <li class="feat-row"><span class="fi fi-yes">✓</span> RSS auto-posting</li>
          <li class="feat-row"><span class="fi fi-yes">✓</span> Full analytics dashboard</li>
          <li class="feat-row"><span class="fi fi-yes">✓</span> Bulk CSV upload</li>
          <li class="feat-row"><span class="fi fi-no">×</span><span class="feat-off">White-label reports</span></li>
