<!-- ========== FAQ ========== -->
<section class="section faq-section" id="faq">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="faq-wrap">
      <div class="center">
        <div class="eyebrow">Questions?</div>
        <h2 class="h2">We've got answers</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-list">

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-q">Does PinFlow follow Pinterest's Terms of Service? <span class="faq-arrow">▾</span></div>
          <div class="faq-a">Yes, completely. PinFlow uses Pinterest's official API exclusively. We don't use scraping, automation bots, or any method that violates Pinterest's ToS — your account is always safe.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-q">Can I manage multiple Pinterest accounts? <span class="faq-arrow">▾</span></div>
          <div class="faq-a">Yes. Pro supports up to 5 accounts and Agency supports up to 20, all from a single clean dashboard. Each account gets its own queue, analytics, and settings.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-q">How does the AI description generator work? <span class="faq-arrow">▾</span></div>
          <div class="faq-a">You give it an image, a link, or a topic. The AI generates a Pinterest-optimized title and description with relevant keywords — in seconds. No copywriting experience needed.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-q">Is there really a free trial with no credit card? <span class="faq-arrow">▾</span></div>
          <div class="faq-a">Absolutely. Every plan starts with a 14-day free trial, full-featured, no credit card required. You only get charged if you decide to continue after the trial ends.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-q">Can I cancel anytime? <span class="faq-arrow">▾</span></div>
          <div class="faq-a">Yes — no contracts, no lock-in. Cancel from your dashboard any time. Annual subscribers keep full access until the end of their billing period.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-q">What payment methods do you accept? <span class="faq-arrow">▾</span></div>
          <div class="faq-a">All major credit cards (Visa, Mastercard, Amex) and PayPal. Payments are processed securely via Stripe.</div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ========== CTA SECTION ========== -->
